review: When my dentist retired, I never thought I would find anyone as compassionate and detail oriented, both Dr. Sanket and Dr. Kanchan are amazing. They along with their staff exceeded my expectation. Very professional, caring and definitely had a way of putting me at ease. They had no idea of the internal anxiety that existed in me with post treatment pain based on previous experiences; in this visit I had no pain post treatments. I am lucky enough to get an appointment with Dr. Sanket and his staff; with his service, one is in very good hands!

review: We contacted the doctor for immediate replacement of my father's dentures. paid 2x the fee. *** ******** ******* ** ********* took 5setting to fit it. dentures broke in less than 1.5 yrs. Avoid this doctor
reply_text:
Hello 
Thank you for ur feedback 
As a denture specialist ( prosthodontist ) 
I had recommended you a correct treatment option 
But we had to choose a compromised treatment option considering ur father's age and other systemic conditions.
It was a well informed decision with ur given consent for the same 
As far as follow up and replacement concerned 
Had recommended you to come for follow up regarding the same 
Happy to help always 
Thank you
